{"tid":157493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係小巴站見到個絲打","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T14:24:45.000Z","uid":17737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95a6062df3d64f4cd220b2e45efd42c0bf3798ae","tid":157493,"uid":17737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"見佢左望右望 以為佢唔知咩站落車 <br />\n諗住問下佢幫下佢 點知佢勁高速講左幾個字<br />\n然後上左車 <br />\n究竟因為我個樣係咪太毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以先唔理我<br />\n希望佢見到個po會回我啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係呀 我落車果時見到係上緊連燈呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f07d712d875b69b262e0bb74de58280437cc1e0","tid":157493,"uid":45459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"係呀 死毒拎 就係見到你個死咸濕樣 嚇撚到我 講左句屌你老母就上左車"}]}